## Agent checklist

- [ ] Query may exceed ~500‚Äì1k prod rows ‚Üí **filtered server pagination**, not only `.limit`.
- [ ] Replacing stray `*` selects with purposeful columns whenever feasible.
- [ ] Listing UI aligns `range`-backed paging with **total matching identical filters**.
- [ ] Oversized `.in("id")` payloads ‚Üí chunked/paginated parents.
- [ ] Aggregation across huge datasets ‚Üí RPC / head counts‚Äînot row dumps.
- [ ] Legacy endpoints still pulling everything flagged as tech debt fixed same PR or tracked with comment tying back here.
